## 🎨 Design Summary

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **Color Palette** | Dark `#0f0f1a` background · Card 1: Purple/Blue · Card 2: Cyan/Green · Card 3: Pink/Amber |
| **Layout** | CSS Grid with `auto-fit` — 3 columns on desktop, stacks to 1 column on mobile |
| **Glassmorphism** | `backdrop-filter: blur(18px)` + semi-transparent `rgba` backgrounds + soft borders |
| **Animations** | Fade-up entrance animation per card · Animated background blobs · 3D tilt on mouse move |
| **Components** | Icon block, badge label, title, description, tags row, stats row, gradient CTA button |
| **Interactions** | Hover lift + scale · 3D parallax mouse-tilt effect · Top gradient border reveal on hover |
| **Customization** | Change emojis, colors in `:root` CSS variables, stat numbers, and button text easily |

